      • initialize

        public void initialize​(java.net.URL url,
                       java.util.ResourceBundle resourceBundle)
        Uses one lambda to search though the allAppointments ObservableList and finds if any appointments are within the next 15 minutes. If an appointment is found within the next 15 minutes the appointmentInfoLabel is set to "Upcoming appointment in 15 minutes or less!" and if no appointment is found the label stays it's default value. Populates allCustomers and allAppointments and then populates the tables with said data
        Specified by:
        initialize in interface javafx.fxml.Initializable
